{%- comment -%}
  Cookie Policy
  Uses isyf-legal-* classes from isyf-base.css
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="isyf-legal-page">
  <div class="isyf-legal-content">
    <h1 class="isyf-legal-title">Cookie Policy</h1>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph"><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>

    <h2 class="isyf-legal-section-title">What Are Cookies</h2>
    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you visit a website. They help the website remember your preferences, understand how you use the site, and improve your browsing experience.</p>

    <h2 class="isyf-legal-section-title">Cookies We Use</h2>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph"><strong>Essential Cookies</strong><br>
    These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly. They enable core features such as navigation, shopping cart functionality, and secure checkout. You cannot opt out of these cookies.</p>
    <ul class="isyf-legal-list">
      <li>Session management and cart persistence</li>
      <li>Security and fraud prevention</li>
      <li>Payment processing</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph"><strong>Analytics Cookies</strong><br>
    These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website by collecting anonymous usage data. This information helps us improve the site experience.</p>
    <ul class="isyf-legal-list">
      <li>Google Analytics - tracks page views, session duration, and user behavior</li>
      <li>Shopify Analytics - monitors store performance and conversion rates</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph"><strong>Marketing Cookies</strong><br>
    These cookies are used to deliver relevant advertisements and track the effectiveness of our marketing campaigns. They may be set by third-party advertising partners.</p>
    <ul class="isyf-legal-list">
      <li>Facebook Pixel - tracks conversions and enables retargeting</li>
      <li>TikTok Pixel - measures ad performance</li>
      <li>Google Ads - delivers targeted advertisements</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="isyf-legal-section-title">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">Our website uses services from the following third parties that may set their own cookies:</p>
    <ul class="isyf-legal-list">
      <li><strong>Shopify Inc.</strong> - e-commerce platform, essential for store operation</li>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> - website analytics and reporting</li>
      <li><strong>Facebook / Meta</strong> - advertising and conversion tracking</li>
      <li><strong>TikTok</strong> - advertising and conversion tracking</li>
      <li><strong>Stripe / PayPal</strong> - payment processing</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="isyf-legal-section-title">How to Manage Cookies</h2>
    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">You can control and manage cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers allow you to:</p>
    <ul class="isyf-legal-list">
      <li>View what cookies are stored and delete them individually</li>
      <li>Block third-party cookies</li>
      <li>Block cookies from specific sites</li>
      <li>Block all cookies</li>
      <li>Delete all cookies when you close your browser</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">Please note that blocking or deleting cookies may affect the functionality of this website and your shopping experience.</p>

    <h2 class="isyf-legal-section-title">Your Consent</h2>
    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">By continuing to use our website, you consent to the use of cookies as described in this policy. You can withdraw your consent at any time by clearing your cookies through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2 class="isyf-legal-section-title">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">If you have any questions about our use of cookies, please contact us:</p>
    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">
      GreenEcoGenius OU<br>
      Tornimae tn 5, Kesklinna linnaosa<br>
      10145 Tallinn, Estonia<br>
      Email: contact@iseeyoufeel.com
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

